LeadParagraph: Samantha Nicole Mirth and Eric Scott Tarr were married Saturday evening at the Chateau at Coindre Hall, an events space in Huntington, N.Y. The Rev. Deb Viola, who is affiliated with the Sanctuary of Peace and Harmony, an interfaith seminary, officiated.
